Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是感冒了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須…須鄉?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人你真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那痛覺還沒有消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須鄉 你已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實接受法律的制裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼完了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我的企業可是數不勝數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 只要完成了研究我就能成為真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為這個世界的神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先要殺了你 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然也敢壞我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你所犯之罪相應的懲罰當然就是死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能是死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼視覺模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我刺不準了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你…明明你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有真正的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須鄉 你不也是一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多薄弱的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠厚重 攻擊範圍又小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但用來殺你已經綽綽有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧 她在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的最後一戰在剛剛結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我還不能聽得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我理解桐人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…終於能見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫結城明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫桐谷和人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 明日奈

